            </tbody>
          </table>

          <p> When you have paid by bank transfer, please send remittance advice to:</p>
          <p>
          <br/>England: madeUpEmail@environment-agency.gov.uk
          <br/>Wales: madeUpEmail@nrw.gov.uk
          <br/>Scotland madeUpEmail@sepa.gov.uk
          <br/>Northern Ireland madeUpEmail@daera-ni.gov.uk
